   <head>Lirica latina - Lirica XXX</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">O rarum formae decus, o lepidissima verba,</l>
     <l n="2">o bene deductum pollice et ore melos!</l>
     <l n="3">An Charitum quarta, an Venus altera, an addita Musis</l>
     <l n="4">est decima, an simul haec Gratia, Musa, Venus?</l>
     <l n="5">Iulia quin sola est, qua cantu Musa, lepore</l>
     <l n="6">Gratia, qua longe est victa decore Venus.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
